scene.message:
Tsurunkamen: Ho ho ho ho...{nl}
Well come, indeed. What sort{nl}
of wares do you require?{waitkey}{ret}

Kamentsurun: Ho ho ho ho...{nl}
Gemstones I love above all{nl}
else.{waitkey}{clearbox}I'm running a blowout trade —{nl}
your gems for my treasured{nl}
wares.{waitkey}Care to give it a try?{waitkey}{ret}

Townsperson: It was such a{nl}
livable town. What in the{nl}
world happened? Am I having{nl}
a bad dream, I wonder.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: A livable town, huh...{nl}
I ought to apologize to the{nl}
townsfolk too.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Shops for the common{nl}
folk have all sorts of rare{nl}
things. Though this town is{nl}
in a class of its own.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: I'm hungry~ But Ayase{nl}
will tough it out. Sonomura's{nl}
having a hard time, after{nl}
all.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: I'm tired from all this{nl}
walking~ ...but this is no{nl}
time to be saying that!{waitkey}{ret}
